      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Budget-Friendly & Ready for the Right Hands \u2014 A Project Car with Potential! This used car is in poor condition, and we're being fully upfront about that. It shows its age with visible wear on the exterior and interior, and it will need some mechanical attention to get it running at its best. That said, it's priced to reflect exactly what it is \u2014 an affordable option for a handy buyer, a first-time driver on a tight budget, or someone looking for a parts vehicle. If you're willing to put in a little work, this could be a solid investment at a very accessible price point!",
