    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 \u2728 **Pristine Mint Condition \u2014 A Rare Opportunity!** We are genuinely excited to offer this exceptional vehicle, and we mean every word: this car is in true mint condition! From the flawless exterior to the spotless interior, everything has been maintained to the highest standard. Mechanically sound and looking showroom-fresh, this is the kind of car that's increasingly hard to find. If you've been searching for a vehicle you can drive with total confidence from day one, your search ends here. Don't miss your chance to own something truly special!",
      "price": 47500.0,
