      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Rare opportunity to own a truly mint-condition vehicle that's as close to showroom-perfect as you'll find on the used market! This car is absolutely immaculate inside and out \u2014 the paint gleams, the interior is spotless, and everything works exactly as it should. Mechanically, it's in outstanding shape with no issues to speak of, and the care put into maintaining this vehicle really shows at every turn. If you've been searching for a used car that feels brand new, your search ends here \u2014 don't miss your chance to drive home in something truly special!",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a solid, dependable car that has been well cared for and is ready for everyday use. The exterior shows minor signs of normal wear, such as light surface scratches or small door dings consistent with regular use, but retains a presentable overall appearance with no major dents or rust concerns. Mechanically, the car runs reliably: the engine starts smoothly, the transmission shifts cleanly, and all major systems \u2014 brakes, cooling, electrical \u2014 are in proper working order. The interior is clean and functional, with typical wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but nothing that detracts significantly from comfort or usability. This is an honest, capable vehicle for a buyer seeking reliable transportation at a fair price, without paying a premium for showroom perfection.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $5,500, a price that honestly reflects its poor condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that means before you consider purchasing. The exterior shows significant wear, including multiple dents, scratches, and rust in several areas. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery, damaged trim, and non-functional components. Mechanically, this car requires substantial attention: it has known issues that will need repair before reliable daily use, and we strongly recommend a pre-purchase inspection by a qualified mechanic. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is comfortable with a significant restoration project, needs it for parts, or has the mechanical expertise to bring it back to working condition. We are pricing it accordingly and are being upfront so there are no surprises \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 a rare find in the used car market and an opportunity not to be missed. From the moment you lay eyes on it, the difference is apparent: the exterior paint is flawless, gleaming with a deep, mirror-like finish free of scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. The body panels are perfectly aligned, the trim is pristine, and every glass surface is crystal clear. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells virtually new \u2014 the seats show no wear, the carpets and headliner are spotless, and every surface, button, and control is in perfect working order. Mechanically, this car is in outstanding shape: the engine starts immediately, runs smoothly and quietly, and delivers strong, confident performance. All systems \u2014 brakes, steering, suspension, HVAC, electronics \u2014 function exactly as intended. Service history is up to date, and there are no known issues, deferred maintenance items, or concerns to disclose. This is a vehicle you can drive home with complete confidence, expecting nothing but reliable, enjoyable performance for years to come.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 33
